# Firebase emulator artifacts
# firebase.devenv*.json is generated by the shared dev environment: the
# Firestore emulator can't read this repo's multi-database firestore
# config, so devenv derives a single-database one beside it at startup.
# One per environment instance, since they share this checkout (api#283).
# See greenearth-social/api#301.
firebase.devenv*.json
